data.description: A charming home in a prime location! This adorable home is in the heart of Alabaster - just minutes from schools and shops with a park right across the street.   Step into the spacious living room with vaulted ceiling and an inviting fireplace as the focal point. The interior shines with fresh paint and the master suite boasts new carpet. Out back the carport can double as a wonderful covered patio entertaining space. This home is turn key and ready for you!
